    <p>The purpose of this activity is for students to choose from activities that offer practice counting and comparing groups of objects and images.</p>
<p>Students choose from any stage of previously introduced centers.</p>
<ul>
      <li>Less, Same, More</li>
      <li>Bingo</li>
